'''Chad''' ke naga lefasaneng la [[Afrika]]. Cameroon e bogarebodikela bja [[Afrika]], e wela seleteng sa [[Bogare bja Afrika|Bogare Bja Afrika]].

Chad e agišane le :
* [[Libya]] (leboa),
* [[Sudan]] (bohlabela),
* [[Central African Republic]] (borwa),
* [[Cameroon]] (borwabodikela),
* [[Nigeria]] (borwabodikela),
* [[Niger]] (bodikela).

